{"tid":226411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚炆！有冇人開道下！","createTime":"2017-05-02T13:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T13:38:30.000Z","uid":72239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a35243d282a70db620c35cc7f0046a218d9cb433","tid":226411,"uid":72239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"有條友 同我幾fd既 同我條女都幾fd<br />\n但條撚屌唔撚話我知就約我條女單獨食飯<br />\n點撚樣呀 識唔識做人嫁<br />\n人地有仔 都單獨約食飯 <br />\n都唔撚知係咪真係當我fd<br />\n約我條女都唔單聲 咩陰謀呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同條女講 唔好同佢食 <br />\n佢就話朋友朋友<br />\n我信我女朋友<br />\n但我真係唔知個撚屌想點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人有相同經歷"},{"pid":"3063fa67e157412afe871b64bdb64fe234379bc7","tid":226411,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"超度就聽過"},{"pid":"9fa1bd0f814af1532f9446034eccfd3380b25d20","tid":226411,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"哀悼就聽過"},{"pid":"070faf3f6b8ade44da5b79599939e9132840dc7f","tid":226411,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"叫你女友帶埋你去<br />\n如果唔係就一齊都唔好去<br />\n識諗嘅就點都會同你一齊去食飯"},{"pid":"92ebf7c2f3869ebf59b48314900d1b33b63dd090","tid":226411,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"盜亦有道"},{"pid":"441b596121557a8c025ed6